author: Orla O'Donnell
title: Covid-19 complacency could be 'disastrous', says Harris
description: Minister for Health Simon Harris has warned that allowing complacency to set in, in efforts to combat Covi-19, could be disastrous and potentially fatal.
content:
Minister for Health Simon Harris has warned that allowing complacency to set in, in efforts to combat Covi-19, could be disastrous and potentially fatal. 
In a video message on Twitter, the minister said the progress made by the Irish people could be undone.… [+2258 chars]
